Description


Instantly and deeply moisturizes;
Aligns the microrelief, reduces the number of wrinkles and reduces their severity;
It has a lifting effect; 
Booster: speeds up the absorption and enhances the effect of other cosmetics;
Gives a feeling of freshness and comfort.
Suggested Use


After cleansing, apply a small amount of toner on the palm of your hand and spread it over the skin of the face, neck and decollete with light tapping movements until completely absorbed.
Key Ingredients

WATER, GLYCERIN, BUTYLENE GLYCOL, ALCOHOL, BETAINE, ADENOSINE, HYDROGENATED LECITHIN, SODIUM HYALURONATE, CERAMIDE 3, HYALURONIC ACID, BIS-PEG-18 METHYL ETHER DIMETHYL SILANE, TREHALOSE, AMMONIUM ACRYLOYLDIMETHYLTAURATE/VP COPOLYMER, PEG-60 HYDROGENATED CASTOR OIL, CAPRYLIC/CAPRIC TRIGLYCERIDE, OCTYLDODECANOL, SACCHARIDE ISOMERATE, SODIUM POLYACRYLATE, CAPRYLYL GLYCOL, 1,2-HEXANEDIOL, RHIZOBIAN GUM, PHENOXYETHANOL, ETHYLHEXYLGLYCERIN, DISODIUM EDTA, FRAGRANCE
